To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private MidPrice _midprice;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_midprice = MIDPRICE(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_midprice.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "midprice", _midprice.Current.Value);
}

symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
